This application consists of the following files:

follower_foreign.hpp  - the h file for the lowest level of the FF interface
follower_foreign.cpp  - the lowest level of the FF interface
follower_interface.cpp - the C++-level interface between QP and the C++ code
follower_interface.ql - declaration of the interface
follower.qlg - the TR program
Makefile - make the C++ code
README - this file


To run

Terminal 1: ros2 launch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_maze.launch.py
Terminal 2: ros2 launch turtlebot3_cartographer cartographer.launch.py use_sim_time:=True

Terminal 3: (TR program without logging)

teleor

| ?~> [follower].

(This will produce some declaration warnings)

| ?~> go().


To terminate Control-D  (getting a segfault when ending - need to track down)

Terminal 3: (TR program with logging - Pedro must be running)

First

logger.py logger&        (creates a app in whick logging messages are displayed)

then

teleor

| ?~> logging logger.

| ?~> [follower].

| ?~> go().
